7501.name: K.H's Letter

^777777''Please don't believe in James, I'm sure he is lying.
I am the one that really loves you.
I may be poor now, but once I succeed in this reseach, I can become even richer than him!
I beg you, come and see me tonight where we first met. I'll be waiting for you.
--K.H. August 19''^000000

7502.name: James's Note
7502.desc:
A letter addressed to Allysia, and written by a man named James.
^777777''Dearest Allysia, Believe me, I was just as surprised to learn that my family engaged me to Ms. Cerinee.
I'm sorry I hurt you, but I've decided that you are the one I want.
Meet me tomorrow night, and we'll run away so that we can finally be together, my love.
--James, August 19th.''^000000

7530.name: Travel Brochure [Amatsu]
7530.desc:
[Amatsu the Land of Destiny]
The people of Amatsu carry themselves with honor and tranquility.
During your visit you should see the Beautiful ^FF0000Water Shrine^000000. The ^FF0000Lord of Amatsu^000000 is much more open
than rulers in other lands, they will talk to visitors and citizens alike.
The ^FF0000Legendary Tree^000000 in Amatsu has many legends about it, such as the Legend that when you propose under
its branches your marriage will be blessed.
While in Amatsu you should see the ^FF0000Coy Pond^000000, nobility of Amatsu keep wonderful gardens or plants, sand and rocks.
Their careful balance and flow reflect the keeper's state of mind.
Part of garden is a Coy Pond, these frolicsome fish are a delight to all.
[Don't forget to take photos of all these things, and show them to your Tour Guide.]

7531.name: Travel Brochure [Kunlun]
7531.desc:
[Kunlun The Hermit Land]
Kunlun is a land in the clouds.
Being so high in the air affords an unprecedented view of the world, it also gives
a different mindset to those whom allow themselves to think freely.
The ^FF0000Statue of Kunlun's Greatest Philosopher^000000, stands proudly in the middle of town, ready to
inspire great thoughts from all those that gaze upon him. All around Kunlun are spectacular ^FF0000Overlooks of the World^000000.
But there are particular spots that are exceptionally breathtaking, please watch your step.
There is a ^FF0000small hill in Kunlun^000000 that is said to of been the Great Philosophers favorite meditation spot,
you should visit there and see if any grand thoughts take you.
No matter how great a culture is, there will always be a few among its citizenry that just don't 'get it'.
Those in Kunlun's history that always thought small eventually truly shrank, and eventually disappeared.
But before that time they had a ^FF0000Mini-town^000000 that they lived in on ground beneath Kunlun.
That place is an object lesson against stagnant thinking.
[Don't forget to take photos of all these things, and show them to your Tour Guide.]

7532.name: Travel Brochure [Louyang]
7532.desc:
[Louyang]
Louyang is a spiritual country, where the warrior spirit and clear thinking are highly prized.
Such wondrous sites such as the ^FF0000Statue of the Man and the Tiger^000000 may inspire you to do your best.
Louyang has a different perspective on healing the mind and the body. While Rune-Midgard relies on the science of potions,
and Faith for healing, the Louyang healers practice their art at a '^FF0000Hospital^000000'.
At a Hospital, your body will be cured by a system of body manipulations and diet.
The beautiful ^FF0000Palace^000000 that is protected by the Great Wall of Louyang is truly a sight to behold for every visitor.
To go along with their proud heritage of Martial Arts and spirit training, they often practice making their bodies
more robust through exercise. Some of these exercises target the legs others the Lungs.
Outside Louyang some practice their ^FF0000Shouting on the Tower^000000. If you have seen all these sites in Louyang,
you will have quite a few good memories to take home.
[Don't forget to take photos of all these things, and show them to your Tour Guide.]

7533.name: Travel Brochure [Ayothaya]
7533.desc:
[Ayothaya]
Thoughts of transcending your limitations, and finding Life's perfect philosophy is Ayothaya's Heritage.
In Ayothaya's history is great Philosopher that all Ayothayans seek to emulate.
There are numerous statues representing this Philosopher exist in and around Ayothaya.
You should visit them to see what differences and significance these ^FF0000Reclining Philosopher Statues^000000 mean to you.
Part of the Philosophy involves many hours of meditation a day to keep balance in your mind and body.
You should visit the ^FF0000Shrine in Ayothaya^000000 and meditate upon your life's journey.
And when you complete your regimen of Exercise and Introspection you can refuel your body by visiting
the ^FF0000Tom Yum Goong restaurant^000000. The famous soup made here is truly delicious.
Don't leave Ayothaya without sampling the dishes there.
[Don't forget to take photos of all these things, and show them to your Tour Guide.]

40251.desc:

- Giving twice more time for ^33CC00Force Sacrifice's^000000 duration and preventing you from dying.

40252.name: Sith Talisman
40252.desc:
Soullinks to Siths.
- Cancels HP penalty from ^33CC00Force Choke^000000 against monsters and boss monsters.
- ^33CC00Force Drain^000000 never fails and doubles its after-cast delay.
- Doubles the chance of inflicting Sleep while using ^33CC00Force Wave^000000.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40253.name: Alchemist Talisman
40253.desc:
Soul Links to Alchemists and Creators.
- Increases effectiveness of ^33CC00Potion Pitcher^000000 by (INT/13)%.
- Allows usage of ^33CC00Aid Berserk^000000 Potion skill.
- Alchemists having Prepare Potion LV 10 are allowed to use ^33CC00Twilight Alchemy^000000 I.
- Allows usage of ^33CC00Twilight Alchemy^000000 skill set.
- Increases effectiveness of ^33CC00Aid Potion^000000 by (INT/13)%.
- All offensive skills and attacks have a (INT/25)% chance of inflicting Burning Status on the target.
- ^33CC00Acid Terror^000000 becomes a splash skill in an area of 4x4 around the targeted player or mob.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40254.name: Assassin Talisman
40254.desc:
Soul Links to Assassins and Assassins Cross.
- Boosting their ^33CC00Sonic Blow^000000 by 150% damage and halving the Cool Down for the skill's duration.
- Has a chance to reflect single target magic back to its caster by 5% chance.
- Boosting their ^33CC00Throw Venom Knife^000000 by 100%.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40255.name: Crusader Talisman
40255.desc:
Soul Links to Crusaders and Paladins.
- Making their ^33CC00Shield Boomerang^000000 never miss, do double the damage, and halving its after cast delay.
- Increase ^33CC00Shield Charge^000000 damage by 60% per skill Level.
- Increase ^33CC00Shield Chain^000000 damage by 150%.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40256.name: Artist Talisman
40256.desc:
Soul Links to Bards, Clowns, Dancers and Gypsies.
- All singing/dancing skills affect the Bard/Dancer him/herself.
- While singing/dancing the walking speed is increased.
- A ^33CC00Whistle^000000 and ^33CC00Humming^000000 linked.
- ^33CC00Assassin Cross of Sunset^000000 and ^33CC00Please Don't Forget Me^000000 linked.
- A ^33CC00Poem of Bragi^000000 and ^33CC00Fortune's Kiss^000000 linked.
- The ^33CC00Apple of Idun^000000 and ^33CC00Service for You^000000 linked.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40257.name: Super Novice Talisman
40257.desc:
Soul Links to Super Novices.
- Super Novices above LV 90 will be temporarily able to equip All Upper/Middle/Lower headgears.
- Super Novices above LV 90 have 1% chance to 'erase' the death record - which means, the last 1% EXP loss will be recovered.
- Super Novices above LV 96 will be temporarily able to equip LV 4 Daggers, 1H Swords, Axes, Maces, and Staffs.
- You can use the skill ^33CC00Act Dead^000000 during the buff.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40258.name: Blacksmith Talisman
40258.desc:
Soul Links to Blacksmiths and Whitesmiths.
- Allowing them to use ^33CC00Full Adrenaline Rush^000000 if they have ^33CC00Adrenaline Rush^000000 LV5 for the skill's duration.
- ^33CC00Full Adrenaline Rush^000000 gives Str +10, Dex +10 and Flee +15.
- ^33CC00Maximum Power Thrust^000000 is buffed with +100% ATK, giving 300% ATK at Level 5.
- Increase ^33CC00Cart Termination^000000 range by 1 cell.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40259.name: Rogue Talisman
40259.desc:
Soul Links to Rogues and Stalkers.
- ^33CC00Dispell^000000 no longer removes your buffs.
- Potions created by someone who is high on the alchemist rank have their effect increased.
- STR bonus from ^33CC00Tunnel Drive^000000 will last 5 minutes and walking speed will also increase.
- Increase ^33CC00Double Strafe^000000 damage by (STR/2)%.
- You can divest through ^33CC00Full Protection^000000 by consuming one Glistening Coat for each attempt (only when the target has ^33CC00Full Protection^000000 activated). It doesn't work with Full Divest but only with ^33CC00Divest Weapon^000000, ^33CC00Shield^000000, ^33CC00Armor^000000 or ^33CC00Helm^000000.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40260.name: Knight Talisman
40260.desc:
Soul Links to Knights and Lord Knights.
- Allowing those who have ^33CC00Two-Hand Quicken^000000 LV 10 to use ^33CC00One-Hand Quicken^000000 for the skill's duration.
- Enable to use Level 10 ^33CC00Parrying^000000 with One-Hand Weapon with a block chance of 2*SkillLV%.
- All skills have their after delay reduced by 40%.
- Increase ^33CC00Spear Boomerang^000000 damage by 200%.
- Increase ^33CC00Spiral Pierce^000000 range by 1 cell.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40261.name: Hunter Talisman
40261.desc:
Soul Links to Hunters and Snipers.
- Effectiveness of ^33CC00Beast Bane^000000 is increased by Hunters/Snipers STR.
- If ^33CC00Double Strafing^000000 is Level 10, a new skill, ^33CC00Beast Strafing^000000, will be available.
- There is a low chance of ^33CC00Falcon Assault^000000 occurring automatically per shot with a bow.
- Increase ^33CC00Double Strafing^000000 damage by 20%.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40262.name: Monk Talisman
40262.desc:
Soul Links to Monks and Champions.
- The ^33CC00Combo Finish^000000 attack becomes a 5x5 cell splash attack.
- SP Cost of combo skills is decreased.
- Allow SP regeneration in ^33CC00Critical Explosion^000000 state.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40263.name: Sage Talisman
40263.desc:
Soul Links to Sages and Professors.
- Allowing their ^33CC00Auto Spell^000000 Skill to always produce LV 10 Bolts if the Sage has learned that much in the Bolt Skill.
- The Sage's HP will also increase by BaseLV * 100 HP and his/her VIT will increase by 35.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40264.name: Priest Talisman
40264.desc:
Soul Links to Priests and High Priests.
- Boosting the power of ^33CC00Holy Light^000000 by +400% but also increasing its SP Cost by +400% for the skill's duration.
- Increase Heal skill's effectiveness by 300%.
- ^33CC00Increase Agility^000000 and ^33CC00Blessing^000000 will turn into an AoE-skill and increases its SP cost by +400%. ^000000
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40265.name: Wizard Talisman
40265.desc:
Soul Links to Wizards and High Wizards.
- Allowing them to cast all Gemstone requiring Skills without using them up (however, it still requires the Wizard to have at least one of the respective Gemstone) for the skill's duration.
- When the Wizard has a 'Crystal Fragment' while under this skill's effect, the item will be used, and any spells that were reflected back to you via Kaite will simply disappear instead of hitting you.
- The Wizard's HP will also increase by BaseLvl * 200 HP and his/her Vit will increase by Int/5. For example, 255 Int will give you an additional bonus of 255/5 = 51 Vit.
- Increase ^33CC00Magic Crasher^000000 Damage by 200%.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40266.name: Ninja Talisman
40266.desc:
Soul Links to Ninja.
- The HP penalty when using the ^33CC00Killing Strike^000000 skill is halved.
- Halves the after-cast delay of ^33CC00Hiding^000000 and ^33CC00Shadow Leap^000000.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40267.name: Gunslinger Talisman
40267.desc:
Soul Links to Gunslinger.
- When using the ^33CC00Rapid Shower^000000 skill there is a chance to knockback the target by 2 cells.
- Ignores all the weapon and bullet requirement for all skills.
^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40268.name: Linker Talisman
40268.desc:

^FFFFFF_^000000
Weight:^009900 1^000000

40269.name: Gladiator Talisman

^FFFFFF_^000000
